title: Michael Jackson Discography (Ogg Vorbis -q1)
description:
Michael Jackson
Discography

- Off The Wall (special edition) (1979 / 2001)
- Thriller (special edition) (1982 / 2001)
- Thriller (25th anniversary edition) (2008)
- Farewell my summer love (LP) (1984)
- Bad (special edition) (1987 / 2001)
- Dangerous (special edition)(1991 / 2001)
- HIStory (2CD) (uncensored) (1995)
- HIStory in the mix (1997)
- Invincible (2001)
- The ultimate collection (2004)
- other songs

All albums EAC secure mode rip -> flac -> ogg vorbis aoTuV -q1, except "farewell my summer love" which was recorded from LP -> MP3 -> ogg vorbis aoTuV -q1.
"other songs" sources were ogg vorbis, mp3 and mpc files.

I excluded "the essential" and "number ones" because all the songs on these compilations are already on the albums which are included in this torrent.

Quality of this collection is good enough for pc speakers, portable use or if you just want to check it out.

I strongly encourage anyone to buy the original albums on CD!

Enjoy this torrent
